$$
V{C}=\frac{n A{\mathrm{Ti}}}{\rho N{\mathrm{A}}}
$$

For HCP, $n=6$ \frac{atoms}{unit} cell, and the atomic weight for $\mathrm{Ti}, A{\mathrm{Ti}}=47.87 \mathrm{~g} / \mathrm{mol}$. Thus,

$$
