& =2.96 \times 10^{-8} \mathrm{~cm}=0.296 \mathrm{~nm}
\end{aligned}
$$

And finally, the value of $c$ is

$c=1.58 a=(1.58)(0.296 \mathrm{~nm})=0.468 \mathrm{~nm}$

