$$
\begin{gathered}
F_{z}=\Delta W \cdot g=0.00005 \times 10^{-3} \times 9.8=-4.9 \times 10^{-7} \mathrm{~N} \\
H=n i=\frac{9 \times 10}{10^{-2}}=9000 \mathrm{~A} / \mathrm{m} \\
