& \rho=4.363 \times 10^{-6} \mathrm{ohm} \cdot \mathrm{~cm} \\
& \sigma=1 / \rho=2.29 \times 10^{5} \mathrm{ohm}^{-1} \cdot \mathrm{~cm}^{-1}
\end{aligned}
$$

(b) At $-100^{\circ} \mathrm{C}$:

$$
